{
  "texts": [
    "We established a robust methodology to ensure the reliability and validity of our ndings.",
    "[5][6][7][8] To determine our 'ground truths', we relied on the comprehensive judgement of a seasoned pediatrician with over a decade of subspecialty experience.",
    "The chatbots' responses were assorted into three separate rounds and randomly presented to expert raters.",
    "To prevent bias and conceal the identity of the chatbots, our experts conducted their assessments on different dates, allowing a substantial 48-hour interval between each rating session.",
    "This methodological rigor was designed to address the bias issue noted in contemporary LLM research [9][10][11].Expanding the scope of our study, we not only assessed the accuracy of the LLM-Chatbots but also evaluated their comprehensiveness and self-correction capabilities."
  ]
}